'''天主教里奧阿查教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Riviascianensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de Riohacha}}）是[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教巴蘭基亞總教區|巴蘭基亞總教區]]。

教區的前身是一個宗座代牧區，於1952年12月4日成立。<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XX |year=1953 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=262-264 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-45-1953-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422193646/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-45-1953-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-22 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>宗座代牧區於1988年6月28日升為教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=RIVIASCIANENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19880628_riviascianensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422190600/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19880628_riviascianensis.html |archivedate=2020-04-22 |language=la |date=1988-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

教區管轄[[瓜希拉省|瓜希拉省]]大部，教座位於該省首府[[里奧阿查|里奧阿查]]，2010年時有900,000名教友（佔轄區總人口83.1%）、23個[[堂區|堂區]]和38名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-de|方濟各·安多尼·塞瓦略斯-埃斯科巴爾|Francisco Antonio Ceballos Escobar}}<ref name="Vatican20200422">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 22.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/22/200422b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422184804/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/22/200422b.html |archivedate=2020-04-22 |language=en |date=2020-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|赫門·拉里奧斯-希梅內斯|Armando Larios Jiménez}}和{{link-es|埃克托·依納爵·薩拉-蘇萊塔|Héctor Ignacio Salah Zuleta}}<ref name="Vatican20200422" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 05.06.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/06/05/0283/00926.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-04-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422185934/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/06/05/0283/00926.html |archivedate=2020-04-22 |language=it |date=2004-06-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

